>> All our textbooks
are in English.

00:36:12.080 --> 00:36:14.600 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow, that must be hard.

00:36:14.600 --> 00:36:16.883 align:middle line:90%
>> Not so hard, I think.

00:36:16.883 --> 00:36:18.300 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm really not
a sports person.

00:36:18.300 --> 00:36:19.298 align:middle line:90%
I really don't like--

00:36:19.298 --> 00:36:21.590 align:middle line:84%
>> You know that there are
people who don't have houses

00:36:21.590 --> 00:36:22.710 align:middle line:90%
to stay?

00:36:22.710 --> 00:36:23.720 align:middle line:90%
They have no food.

00:36:23.720 --> 00:36:25.440 align:middle line:90%
They have no clothing to wear.

00:36:25.440 --> 00:36:28.350 align:middle line:84%
>> Adults think I'm kind
of shy, because I'm quiet.

00:36:28.350 --> 00:36:30.200 align:middle line:90%
But I'm really not shy at all.

00:36:30.200 --> 00:36:32.890 align:middle line:90%
>> Same with me.

00:36:32.890 --> 00:36:33.740 align:middle line:90%
>> --A lot.

00:36:33.740 --> 00:36:36.870 align:middle line:84%
And random things can
happen that make me bust

00:36:36.870 --> 00:36:38.040 align:middle line:90%
into song and start singing.

00:36:38.040 --> 00:36:43.570 align:middle line:90%


00:36:43.570 --> 00:36:46.870 align:middle line:84%
>> What I like to do is look
at different religions and pick

00:36:46.870 --> 00:36:47.860 align:middle line:90%
what I like from them.

00:36:47.860 --> 00:36:49.610 align:middle line:90%
So I like Jesus.

00:36:49.610 --> 00:36:51.950 align:middle line:90%
Like, if you read--

00:36:51.950 --> 00:36:55.945 align:middle line:84%
do you have a world
religions class or?

00:36:55.945 --> 00:36:58.867 align:middle line:84%
>> Just the word "religion,"
especially in America,

00:36:58.867 --> 00:37:02.032 align:middle line:84%
it's such a powerful word
that people don't really want

00:37:02.032 --> 00:37:04.612 align:middle line:84%
to talk about it, because
everybody in America tries

00:37:04.612 --> 00:37:06.400 align:middle line:90%
to be so politically correct.

00:37:06.400 --> 00:37:13.380 align:middle line:84%
>> I feel that happiness
is naturally originated

00:37:13.380 --> 00:37:14.600 align:middle line:90%
in one's mind.

00:37:14.600 --> 00:37:18.350 align:middle line:84%
>> Because, really, it's
the change inside ourselves

00:37:18.350 --> 00:37:21.430 align:middle line:84%
